author: David Sigston
title: Qld man in custody after ramming office - Yahoo7
text:
Share Qld man in custody after ramming office - Yahoo7 Police have arrested a man who allegedly reversed his car into a child safety service centre west of Brisbane. 
It's alleged he reversed into the office building in Forest Lake just before 9am on Tuesday. 
There was slight damage to the building but no one was injured.
